li id=\"cite_note-davidson-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-davidson_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-davidson_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Davidson, Ian (2004). <i>Voltaire in Exile</i>. Atlantic books. pp.&#160;159\u2013164. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1843540878\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1843540878\">1843540878</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Voltaire+in+Exile&amp;rft.pages=159-164&amp;rft.pub=Atlantic+books&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=1843540878&amp;rft.aulast=Davidson&amp;rft.aufirst=Ian&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APr%C3%A9cis+du+si%C3%A8cle+de+Louis+XV\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Le Morillon, Sebastien R. (30 November 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.historytoday.com/sebastien-r-le-morillon/rethinking-napoleon%E2%80%99s-roots\">\"Rethinking Napoleon's Roots\"</a>. <i>History Today</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">9 June</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=History+Today&amp;rft.atitle=Rethinking+Napoleon%E2%80%99s+Roots&amp;rft.date=2015-11-30&amp;rft.aulast=Le+Morillon&amp;rft.aufirst=Sebastien+R.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.historytoday.com%2Fsebastien-r-le-morillon%2Frethinking-napoleon%25E2%2580%2599s-roots&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APr%C3%A9cis+du+si%C3%A8cle+de+Louis+XV\" class